node.text:
My Etsy shop is open from Sept 3 to 17 💫

There is free shipping for all the items listed at my shop from USA orders of $35 and above. I send internationally as well, but some countries may have restrictions. Thus, causing a delay than the estimated time. Tracking are only available for USA orders. I hope you enjoy and thank you for your support! It means a lot. Link in bio ♥️

Prints are made once ordered. 

P.S. I am just one person handling this shop, so please understand that it’ll take time to process your purchase. 

#jyundee #digitalpainting #artwork #fanart #cartoon #drawing

node.text:
Hello! Here is a NEW #DTIYS 😁

RULES:
🌷tag me on your post. 
🌷use #jyundeeart and #drawthisinyourstyle on the post description.
🌷post the 2nd image on the second slide of yours.
🌷you can change the expression and pose, hair, etc. as along as she is still recognizable. 
🌷you can paint digitally and traditionally 

❗️Challenged will end on Sept 24❗️

I will be sharing some of my favorites on my stories and include it into my highlight section of my profile. 

Have fun!! ♥️

#jyundee #digitalpainting #semirealism #characterart #fantasyart #painting #fashion

node.text:
August patreon physicals ✨

Tier 3: Gwen vinyl 
Tier 5: Gwen vinyl + OceanHero glitter vinyl + signed A5 print 

These will be available until the end of August. I send domestically and internationally; however it is standard ship and does not have tracking. Within the perk, you’ll also get access to digital perks such as original painting files, HD unwatermark, painting videos and tutorial +. This month’s digital perks is still in process and I usually get them done by the last week of the month. 

I am currently short on Gwen, so I reordered some more. 

#tdi #totaldramaisland #digitalpainting #semirealism #jyundee #characterart #fashion
